import React, { useRef, useState } from 'react'
import {Typography, TextField, Grid, Container, Paper} from '@mui/material';

const GridOptions = [
    {name : "username", lab : "username"},
    {name : "email", lab : "email"},
    {name : "password", lab : "password"},
    {name : "first_name", lab : "first_name"},
    {name : "last_name", lab : "last_name"},
    {name : "address", lab : "address"},
    {name : "city", lab : "city"},
    {name : "State", lab : "State"},
    {name : "Country", lab : "Country"},
    {name : "phone", lab : "phone"}
]

function Register() {
    return (
        <Container component="main" maxWidth="sm" sx={{ my: 8}}>
        <Paper variant="outlined" sx={{ my: { xs: 3, md: 6 }, p: { xs: 2, md: 3 }, bgcolor:'silver' }}>
        <React.Fragment>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom sx={{mb:5}}>
                Register : 
            </Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={3}>
                {

                }
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                    <TextField
                        required
                        id="firstName"
                        name="firstName"
                        label="First name"
                        fullWidth
                        variant="standard"
                    />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
                    <TextField
                        required
                        id="lastName"
                        name="lastName"
                        label="Last name"
                        fullWidth
                        autoComplete="family-name"
                        variant="standard"
                    />
                </Grid>
            </Grid>
        </React.Fragment>
        </Paper>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Register
